Package org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.json.jackson.datavalues

Class JacksonInnerEntityId

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.json.jackson.datavalues.JacksonInnerEntityId

  • public class JacksonInnerEntityId
extends Object
    This class represents the inner anonymous object in the JSON type of "wikibase-entityid". Not to be confused with the entityId of the main document.
    Author:
    Fredo Erxleben, Thomas Pellissier Tanon

      • getStringId

        public String getStringId​()
                   throws IllegalArgumentException
        Returns the standard string version of the entity id encoded in this value. For example, an id with entityType "item" and numericId "42" is normally identified as "Q42".
        Returns:
        the string id
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the entity type of this value is unknown and can thus not be mapped to a string id
